{"tid":484070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社區組織協會：單程證人士可填補基層勞動力不足","createTime":"2017-11-29T17:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T12:40:15.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e76a905b3e8e74c0fa52e8aec90a74722fa3655","tid":484070,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"持單程證來港人數創十年新高　議員質疑內地壟斷審批權 <br />\n2017-11-29 HKT 18:19 <br />\n<br />\n保安局資料顯示，去年有5萬7千多人持單程證從來港，是過去10年以來最多，而45歲以上人士10年來的增幅，較年輕組別人士高。 <br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會說，單程證來港的多數是「超齡子女」或者與配偶團聚，這批中年人士可填補基層勞動力不足的問題。 <br />\n<br />\n議員張超雄就認為，內地政府壟斷審批權不合理，又要求當局盡快解釋去年單程證打破150個配額的原因。"},{"pid":"d378ed1e8eb2eebeca1be6cbabf41bd151367dbb","tid":484070,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"有「基層勞動力不足」<br />\n想問幾時先有「基層勞動力充足」？"},{"pid":"4a31ca3d13819d050891b376dd25160babc5cb92","tid":484070,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"不過填補埋公屋既空缺"},{"pid":"5bf65542ca290e942cde88672a22611336197230","tid":484070,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:16:49.000Z","msg":"但果班單程證走哂去申請綜援"},{"pid":"981ea0050d273660879eab721ab4f6f9b9584a65","tid":484070,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但果班<span style=\"color: red;\">每日150隻蝗</span>走哂去申請綜援</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e40913fd723b3cf495e1daa7c9f2a1facfc5177e","tid":484070,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"攞綜援補你老母咩！"},{"pid":"23bb394cc10bc0d6162b24c2f1f9fc38da8baca4","tid":484070,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2F